{"tid":530441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【人生贏家】18歲首次置業　32歲地產大亨擁200個物業","createTime":"2018-01-15T18:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T23:17:12.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"22b14357ea5a43ae2e7738e9ab8815f77aa78240","tid":530441,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T18:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180115/large/1516003667_d526.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180115%2Flarge%2F1516003667_d526.jpg&h=e6031eae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳洲悉尼一名地產大亨年僅32歲，就坐擁逾200棟物業，18歲已首次置業的他，如今擁有的物業估值已達5,500萬澳元（約3.4億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n伯奇（Nathan Birch）的投資策略是長線持有，以低價買入，之後放租並慢慢加租，再伺機以扣除按揭後得來的利潤再買新物業，以錢滾錢方式慢慢壯大自己的物業王國。如今他持有的某些物業已升值一倍。<br />\n<br />\n雖然坐擁逾百棟物業，但伯奇未為母親買一間屋，對方繼續住在交通不便的德鲁伊特山（Mt Druitt）的舊屋，不過這並非他不孝，伯奇的母親說：「因為我不需要一間屋，我的小屋很好，我常常都這樣說。」伯奇稱一直想買間夢想之家與母親同住，但對方表示在舊屋住得很開心。<br />\n<br />\n伯奇又表示會繼續添置物業，未來準備針對黃金海岸的房地產出手，認為該處有巨大的升值潛力，「那裡就像是澳洲的邁阿密，仍是環球金融危機後的價錢，仍然很低。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180116/57706894\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180116%2F57706894&d=WyiZAUpg5RWpngKUq%2FFX%2B%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=a448ba5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180116%2F57706894&h=1830fa61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180116/57706894</a>"},{"pid":"dfe427078d1f2e76d3a2a41afd0d8471104e93c4","tid":530441,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T20:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3999dbf8fc6081d7cffc3952758e952f272a853d","tid":530441,"uid":48579,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T21:04:09.000Z","msg":"人地200棟先值3.4億港紙 <br />\n香港樓價真係痴撚線"},{"pid":"fd727103e5d66a2cb5820ca50633f25baaa00b07","tid":530441,"uid":8000,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T21:12:32.000Z","msg":"香港一棟 講緊真係一棟<br />\n3.4億你買得一忽仔咋傻仔"},{"pid":"2d7dee7afa513f6428019d52e01cd03bd60cfada","tid":530441,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T23:02:01.000Z","msg":"除返開先170萬港紙一，記者係咪計錯數啊，悉尼邊有咁平啊。"},{"pid":"be03ab71eed8c7bd65d991d914e0e7e3c81b4700","tid":530441,"uid":165052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd727103e5d66a2cb5820ca50633f25baaa00b07","tid":530441,"uid":8000,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T21:12:32.000Z","msg":"香港一棟 講緊真係一棟<br />\n3.4億你買得一忽仔咋傻仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T23:14:06.000Z","msg":"邊個話緊邊個傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 納米樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606f00ef6451733b4f50727f2b027911d7388f3d","tid":530441,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T23:16:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ce2481d71d878e0ab764966a844c05c4ad8e637","tid":530441,"uid":132249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d7dee7afa513f6428019d52e01cd03bd60cfada","tid":530441,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T23:02:01.000Z","msg":"除返開先170萬港紙一，記者係咪計錯數啊，悉尼邊有咁平啊。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T23:17:12.000Z","msg":"可能係啲好遠既suburb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}